          He had systems, stock responses, and ways of organizing knowledge long before tools like this existed.
        </p>

        <p style={styles.text}>
          He was doing, in a human way, what AI is just starting to do now.
        </p>

        <p style={styles.text}>
          VIC is my way of continuing that idea — bringing real teaching into a modern tool.
        </p>

        <p style={styles.text}>
          I’ve spent my career in education — as a principal, teacher, and someone who’s worked directly with students and families.
          VIC is built from that experience, not just technology.
        </p>

        <p style={styles.text}>
          The goal is simple:
